    "content": "<h1>Active Workforce Pro (AWP) Registration Agreement</h1><p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 17/03/2025</p><p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 10/03/2025</p><p>This AWP Registration Agreement (Agreement) sets forth the terms and conditions of your use of the Active Workforce Pro (AWP) App and related services (Services) between you (the employee, security guard, or authorised representative) and ICORP Security (Company, we, our, or us). By registering, accessing, or using the AWP App, you agree to comply with this Agreement.</p><p>It is important that you read and understand the following terms. By clicking AGREE, you confirm that you have read and understood this Agreement and consent to the terms outlined. If you do not agree, you must not access or use the AWP App.</p><h3>1. Service Description</h3><ul><li>Identity verification through selfie photos</li><li>Location tracking at sign-in and sign-out</li><li>Shift management and compliance with ICORP Security operational requirements</li></ul><h3>2. Data Collection and Privacy</h3><p>In line with Australian privacy laws, ICORP Security is committed to protecting the personal information of employees. As detailed in our Privacy Policy, the following data will be collected when using the AWP App:</p><ul><li><strong>Selfie Photo:</strong> Used for identity verification at sign-in and sign-out.</li><li><strong>Location Data (Longitude & Latitude):</strong> Collected at sign-in and sign-out to confirm your physical presence at assigned work locations.</li></ul><p>This data will be stored securely, used only for operational and compliance purposes, and will not be shared with third parties unless required by law.</p><p>For full details, refer to our <a href=\"https://activeworkforcepro.com.au/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p><h3>3. Account Registration and Use</h3><h4>3.1 Eligibility</h4><ul><li>You must be an authorised employee of ICORP Security to use the AWP App.</li><li>You must not be barred from receiving these services under Australian law.</li></ul><h3>4. Terms of Use</h3><p>When using the AWP App, you must comply with all policies:</p><ul><li>Comply with Australian laws and ICORP Security policies.</li><li>Use the App only for work-related purposes.</li><li>Accurately sign in and sign out at your assigned location.</li><li>Not share, falsify, or manipulate location data or selfie photos.</li></ul><h3>5. Service Updates & Modifications</h3><p>ICORP Security may update or modify the AWP App as needed.</p><h3>6. Data Retention and Security</h3><p>ICORP Security ensures encryption and secure storage of all collected data. Employee data is retained only as long as necessary for operational, payroll, and legal compliance.</p><h3>7. Termination of Use</h3><p>You may request account closure by submitting a formal request to HR at <a href=\"mailto:operations@icorpsecurity.com.au\">operations@icorpsecurity.com.au</a>.</p><h3>8. Limitation of Liability</h3><p>ICORP Security is not liable for any technical issues beyond our control.</p><h3>9. Dispute Resolution</h3><p>This Agreement is governed by the laws of Australia.</p><h3>10. Agreement Updates</h3><p>ICORP Security may update or modify this Agreement.</p><h3>11. Contact Information</h3><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:operations@icorpsecurity.com.au\">operations@icorpsecurity.com.au</a></p><p>Phone: 1300 84 84 50</p>"
